headline.print_headline: Street Case Will Go to Court
headline.main: Picabo Street Case Will Go to Court

snippet: Street, an Olympic gold medal skier, is headed for a May trial on misdemeanor domestic violence charges. Her lawyer said she turned down a plea deal.
lead_paragraph: Street, an Olympic gold medal skier, is headed for a May trial on misdemeanor domestic violence charges. Her lawyer said she turned down a plea deal.
